sigkdd#Hotel: The Main office is the parent of the Hotel which is the parent of the Place.
sigkdd#Place: Main office is parented by Conference hall and Conference hall.
sigkdd#Abstract: Deadline Paper Submission is designed by ACM SIGKDD and is submitted until the Deadline. The document is presented by a speaker who is the parent of Deadline Paper Submission. Deadline Paper Submission is also the parent of Thing and ACM SIGKDD.
sigkdd#Document: ACM SIGKDD is the parent of Thing and Deadline Abstract Submission. Deadline Abstract Submission is the child of Review which is submitted until the Deadline.
sigkdd#Deadline_Abstract_Submission: Deadline Abstract Submission is the parent of Deadline which was designed by ACM SIGKDD. ACM SIGKDD holds the Thing Conference and also holds Deadline Abstract Submission.
sigkdd#Best_Applications_Paper_Award: The Best Applications Paper Award is awarded by the Organizator. The Organizator is the parent of the person who is the parent of the Thing and the Best Research Paper Award.
sigkdd#Award: The Best Student Paper Award is the parent of the Best Research Paper Award. The Award is also the child of the Best Research Paper Award.
sigkdd#Deadline_Paper_Submission: Deadline is the parent of Deadline Paper Submission and Deadline Abstract Submission. Deadline Author notification is the parent of Deadline and Deadline Abstract Submission.
sigkdd#Deadline: Deadline was designed by ACM SIGKDD and is the child of Deadline Author notification. Deadline is the parent of Thing.
sigkdd#Deadline_Author_notification: Deadline is the child of ACM SIGKDD who is the parent of Thing. The Deadline Author notification was designed by ACM SIGKDD.
sigkdd#Webmaster: The Webmaster is the parent of the Organizator who is the child of the Program Chair and the Program Committee member. The Organizator is the child of the Program Chair and the Program Committee member.
sigkdd#Organizator: The Organizator is the parent of the Program Chair and the Organizator is the child of the Sponzor fee. The registration fee is also the parent of the Organizator who is also the child of the Sponzor fee.
sigkdd#Author_of_paper_student: The Best Student Paper Award is the parent of the Award which is the best student paper award. The Award is also the child of the Best Applications Paper Award.
sigkdd#Best_Student_Paper_Award: The Best Student Paper Award is the parent of the Award. It is also the child of the Best Research Paper Award and the Best Applications Paper Award.
sigkdd#Author: The author of paper student is the child of the parent of the speaker who is the parent of the person who is the parent of the speaker. The listener is the child of the author and the writer is the parent of the person who is the author of the Thing.
sigkdd#ACM_SIGKDD: ACM SIGKDD is the parent of Sponzor who is the child of Gold Supporter. The parent of Sponzor is Gold Supporter. The Fee is the parent of Sponzor who is the child of the registration fee.
sigkdd#Conference: The conference is held by ACM SIGKDD which is the parent of Thing.
sigkdd#Sponzor: Sponzor is the child of Bronze Supporter and the Exhibitor.
sigkdd#Exhibitor: Sponzor is a child of ACM SIGKDD and is the parent of Exhibitor. ACM SIGKDD holds the Conference which is held by ACM SIGKDD.
sigkdd#Registration_SIGMOD_Member: The registration fee for SIGMOD members is the same as for Sponzor fee. The registration student is the parent of the registration fee and the registration student is the parent of the registration fee.
sigkdd#Registration_fee: Fee is the parent of registration fee and Sponzor fee. Fee is the child of registration fee and Sponzor fee.
sigkdd#Person: The speaker is the child of the General Chair and the Invited Speaker. The speaker is the parent of the General Chair and the Organizator is the child of the Speaker.
sigkdd#Bronze_Supporter: Sponzor is the child of Bronze Supporter and Exhibitor.
sigkdd#Committee: The Organizing Committee is the parent of the Committee which is the child of the Program Committee and the Organizing Committee.
sigkdd#Platinum_Supporter: Sponzor is a child of Silver Supporter and ACM SIGKDD. Sponzor is the parent of Thing and is searched by ACM SIGKDD.
sigkdd#Conference_hall: The Conference Hall is parented by the Hotel which is the parent of the Conference Hall.
sigkdd#Best_Paper_Awards_Committee: The Best Paper Awards Committee is the parent of the Organizing Committee and the Organizing Committee. The Committee is also the child of the Organizing Committee.
sigkdd#Program_Chair: The program chair is the parent of the Organizator who is the child of the Webmaster. The Organizator is the child of the main office and the hotel. The registration fee is paid by the person who is the child of the SIGKDD member.
sigkdd#Main_office: The main office is parented by the Conference hall and the Hotel which is also parented by the Conference hall.
sigkdd#Registration_Non-Member: The registration fee for a non-member is the registration fee. The registration fee is the parent of the Fee and the child of the Sponzor fee.
sigkdd#Fee: Sponzor and registration student are both parents of the same person. The latter is the parent of the Thing and the other is the parent of the Hotel which is the parent of the Place. The registration fee is paid by the person who can stay in the Hotel.
sigkdd#Review: The Deadline for Deadline Paper Submission is the parent of the document which is submitted by the speaker. The speaker is the child of the listener and the child of the Invited Speaker. The Deadline for Deadline Paper Submission is the Deadline for the presentation of the document by the speaker.
sigkdd#Sponzor_fee: Fee is the parent of Sponzor fee and registration fee. Fee is also the parent of Fee.
sigkdd#Registration_SIGKDD_Member: The registration fee for SIGKDD members is paid by the parent of the registered non-member who is the parent of Thing. The registration fee is also paid by the registered non-member who is the parent of the registered member.
sigkdd#Program_Committee: The Organizing Committee is the parent of the Organizing Committee and the Program Committee. The Committee is also the child of the Organizing Committee.
sigkdd#General_Chair: The General Chair is the parent of the Organizator who is a child of the Program Committee member and the General Chair.
sigkdd#Speaker: The parent of a speaker is a Thing.
sigkdd#Gold_Supporter: Gold Supporter is the parent of Sponzor who is a child of Gold Supporter. He also pays the Sponzor fee which is a part of the registration fee.
sigkdd#Registration_Student: The Registration Student is the parent of the Registration fee which is paid by the person who is the child of the Registration SIGKDD Member and the parent of Thing.
sigkdd#Organizing_Committee: The Organizing Committee is the parent of the Best Paper Awards Committee. The Committee is also the child of the Organizing Committee.
sigkdd#Listener: The parent of the listener is the Organizator. The Organizator is the parent of the Webmaster and the General Chair. The main office is the parent of the Conference hall and the Organizator is the parent of the Webmaster. The parent of the listener is the Organizator who can stay in the place.
sigkdd#Program_Committee_member: The Organizator is the child of the Program Chair and the Organizator. The Organizator is the parent of the Program Chair and the Organizator is the child of the Registration Non-Member. The Registration fee is paid by the Organizator and the Organizator is the child of the Program Chair.
sigkdd#Invited_Speaker: The speaker is the parent of the child of the Listener and the child of the Invited Speaker. The speaker is also the parent of the person who is the parent of the Thing.
sigkdd#Best_Research_Paper_Award: The best research paper award is awarded by the Organizator. The Organizator is the parent of the speaker and the child of Thing.
sigkdd#Best_Student_Paper_Supporter: Sponzor is the parent of Silver Supporter and the best student paper supporter. Sponzor is also the parent of the registration fee and the Sponzor fee.
sigkdd#Paper: Deadline Paper Submission is the parent of Document which is also known as Abstract. The Deadline Paper Submission is the parent of Deadline Paper Submission and Deadline Paper Submission is the Deadline.
sigkdd#Silver_Supporter: Sponzor is the parent of the Silver Supporter and the child of the Exhibitor. Sponzor is the parent of the Fee and the registration fee.
sigkdd#Organizing_Committee_member: The Organizing Committee member is the parent of the Organizator. The Organizator is the child of the Organizator and the parent of Thing.
sigkdd#Author_of_paper: The Best Research Paper Award is the parent of the Best Student Paper Award. The award is the child of the Best Research Paper Award and the author of the paper is the author of the Best Applications Paper Award.
